{"tid":1957141,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"引退一年出新作 吉澤明步自傳《單體女優》","createTime":"2020-04-03T16:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T16:39:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa34d88e4001cb7225d6a6935ff6f80e183223a","tid":1957141,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"上年3月，一代名女優吉澤明步正式引退，相信唔少男士都相當婉惜。慶幸嘅係入行16年、名下有427品作品（維基百科有人整理出完整片單）、而且於AV本業外亦涉足藝能界嘅佢，喺引退後發展得都唔錯，除咗主持電台節目，最近亦推出自傳式小說《單體女優》。<br />\n<br />\n《單體女優》一書以吉澤明步自身經歷為主軸，全書六個章節由她入行前、18歲初入行，講到生涯後期嘅「惠比壽麝香葡萄」年代，其中第三章「租借AV的洗禮」及第四章「DVD中開花」更加係側面描述緊AV業界嘅變遷。她亦透露當年係瞞住父母入行，後來被發現時當然大吵一場；另外17歲先破瓜，入行前只曾有一個性伴嘅佢，入行16年來與4個男朋友的情史。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/thezone/23511?fbclid=IwAR27X3OQ8grGfssvY3tACIdAW2Sy5zoSlDKF7MuYOSzdl-j7-5auhMZL528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fthezone%2F23511%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR27X3OQ8grGfssvY3tACIdAW2Sy5zoSlDKF7MuYOSzdl-j7-5auhMZL528&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQynqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=4c56a0c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/thezone/23511?fbclid=IwAR27X3OQ8grGfssvY3tACIdAW2Sy5zoSlDKF7MuYOSzdl-j7-5auhMZL528</a>"},{"pid":"6d8887954b497635e1ae9f59979bcc1b0806ecec","tid":1957141,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/4/3/fc03b9d536d756b7083a2b36f73c33c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F4%2F3%2Ffc03b9d536d756b7083a2b36f73c33c5.jpg&h=6c434956&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aad7b96619cd34509f3297d9134ae74dc301d61d","tid":1957141,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421adcbf1c511c05f21a891a1487469b7e07d8ba","tid":1957141,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"